>{<span class=\"fn\">a </span><span class=\"fn\">b </span><span class=\"fn\">c</span> : <span class=\"fn\">σ</span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">h</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">f</span> <span class=\"fn\">a</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">f</span> <span class=\"fn\">b</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Computability/StateTransition.html#StateTransition.Reaches₁\">Reaches₁</a> <span class=\"fn\">f</span> <span class=\"fn\">a</span> <span class=\"fn\">c</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Core.html#Iff\">↔</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Computability/StateTransition.html#StateTransition.Reaches₁\">Reaches₁</a> <span class=\"fn\">f</span> <span class=\"fn\">b</span> <span class=\"fn\">c</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Mathlib/Computability/StateTransition.html#StateTransition.reaches₁_eq","kind":"theorem","line":48,"name":"StateTransition.reaches₁_eq","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Computability/StateTransition.lean#L48-L50"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Computability/StateTransition.html#StateTransition.Reaches₁\"><span class=\"name\">StateTransition</span>.<span class=\"name\">Reaches₁</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">σ</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">f</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">σ</span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <span class=\"fn\">σ</span></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">σ</span> → <span class=\"fn\">σ</span> → <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Prop</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The transitive closure of a state transition function. `Reaches₁ f a b` means there is a\nnonempty finite sequence of steps `f a = some a₁`, `f a₁ = some a₂`, ... such that `aₙ = b`.\nThis relation does not permit zero steps of the state transition function. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Computability/StateTransition.html#StateTransition.Reaches₁","kind":"def","line":42,"name":"StateTransition.Reaches₁","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Computability/StateTransition.lean#L42-L46"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Computability/StateTransition.html#StateTransition.Reaches\"><span class=\"name\">StateTransition</span>.<span class=\"name\">Reaches</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">σ</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">f</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">σ</span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <span class=\"fn\">σ</span></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">σ</span> → <span class=\"fn\">σ</span> → <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Prop</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The reflexive transitive closure of a state transition function. `Reaches f a b` means\nthere is a finite sequence of steps `f a = some a₁`, `f a₁ = some a₂`, ... such that `aₙ = b`.\nThis relation permits zero steps of the state transition function. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Computability/StateTransition.html#StateTransition.Reaches","kind":"def","line":36,"name":"StateTransition.Reaches","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Computability/StateTransition.lean#L36-L40"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Computability/StateTransition.html#StateTransition.eval\"><span class=\"name\">StateTransition</span>.<span class=\"name\">eval</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">σ</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">f</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">σ</span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <span class=\"fn\">σ</span></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">σ</span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Part.html#Part\">Part</a> <span class=\"fn\">σ</span></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Run a state transition function `σ → Option σ` \"to completion\". The return value is the last\nstate returned before a `none` result. If the state transition function always returns `some`,\nthen the computation diverges, returning `Part.none`. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Computability/StateTransition.html#StateTransition.eval","kind":"def","line":30,"name":"StateTransition.eval","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Computability/StateTransition.lean#L30-L34"}}],"imports":["Init","Mathlib.Algebra.Order.Group.Nat","Mathlib.Data.PFun","Mathlib.Computability.Tape","Mathlib.Data.Finset.Option","Mathlib.Data.Finset.Prod","Mathlib.Data.Fintype.Defs"],"instances":[],"name":"Mathlib.Computability.StateTransition"}